Directly adjacent Westfield’s Belconnen Mall and the Lake Ginninderra foreshore, the property is ideally situated to meet all the needs of its occupants and visitors. The Belconnen Bus Interchange is only 300m* away and a taxi rank only 100m* from the site.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Northpoint Plaza commands a highly visible location in the heart of the Belconnen Town Centre. Immediately adjacent to the Westfield Shopping Centre, with a mixture of office and shop front tenancies, Northpoint Plaza offers the perfect environment for both professional offices and businesses requiring shop frontage.

Ample public parking is available nearby as well as secure basement parking for tenants.

Available now:

Ground Suite 1: 60sqm* Retail space with great exposure onto Chandler Street.

Ground Suite 2: 107sqm* Internal retail or office space ready for fitout.

Level 1 Suite 1: 785sqm* Open plan space ready for fitout which is sub-dividable to meet requirements.

For further information or to arrange an inspection please contact CBRE.

*Approx.

Belconnen Commercial Chambers is a mixed-use commercial building directly across from the Belconnen bus interchange. This two-storey development is home to retail on the ground floor as well as quality first floor offices.

Available for lease are level one office spaces ranging from 46-228sqm, all of which feature modern fitouts with access to a communal kitchen and shower facilities. 


For more information or to arrange an inspection please contact CBRE Canberra.
